EscapeHatchGettersTest
├── when calling getCurrentHatch
│   └── it should return the current hatch based on current epoch
├── when calling getHatch
│   └── it should return epoch / FREQUENCY
├── when calling getFirstEpoch
│   └── it should return hatch * FREQUENCY
├── when calling getDesignatedProposer
│   └── it should return the designated proposer for the hatch
├── when calling isHatchPrepared
│   ├── given hatch has been prepared
│   │   └── it should return true
│   └── given hatch has not been prepared
│       └── it should return false
├── when calling getCandidateInfo
│   └── it should return correct data through full lifecycle
├── when calling getCandidateCount
│   └── it should return the current number of active candidates
├── when calling getCandidateCountForHatch
│   └── it should return the number of candidates in the snapshot for the target hatch
├── when calling getCandidateAtIndex
│   └── it should return the candidate address at the given index
├── when calling getCandidateAtIndexForHatch
│   ├── given freeze timestamp has passed
│   │   └── it should return the candidate address from the snapshot at the given index
│   └── given freeze timestamp has not passed
│       └── it should revert with SetUnstable
├── when calling isCandidate
│   ├── given address is in active candidate set
│   │   └── it should return true
│   └── given address is not in active candidate set
│       └── it should return false
├── when calling getSetTimestamp
│   └── it should return the timestamp when candidate set freezes for the target hatch
├── when calling getSeedTimestamp
│   └── it should return the timestamp when RANDAO seed is sampled for the target hatch
├── when calling getRollup
│   └── it should return the ROLLUP address
├── when calling getBondToken
│   └── it should return the BOND_TOKEN address
├── when calling getBondSize
│   └── it should return the BOND_SIZE value
├── when calling getWithdrawalTax
│   └── it should return the WITHDRAWAL_TAX value
├── when calling getFailedHatchPunishment
│   └── it should return the FAILED_HATCH_PUNISHMENT value
├── when calling getFrequency
│   └── it should return the FREQUENCY value
├── when calling getActiveDuration
│   └── it should return the ACTIVE_DURATION value
├── when calling getLagInHatches
│   └── it should return the LAG_IN_HATCHES value
└── when calling getProposingExitDelay
    └── it should return the PROPOSING_EXIT_DELAY value
